reviews.review_text: Awesome Remembered this date as one of my favorite live show cassettes from my old car in the eighties. I thought thaud quality was ok, good in the first set with Row Jimmy and Jack Straw but then it just got better with Weather Report -> China Doll and by Dark Star -> Spanish Jam it is absolutely mind-blowing. Good to have in its entirety for historical value even if the tuning gaps are tedious but I will be moving the above mentioned mp3s to my pod for sure. Very fine taping job esp. second set. You can't beat AUD tapes for recreating the feeling of being there.

Great Weather Down In Miami amazing show.. the nite B4 isnt bad either. 
 Thnks Tazermun
Jerry will certainly give yah goose bumps ... I.m On My WAy.;0)

Thanks Archive Great sounding aud and a great 74 show with the band delivering a tight and at times very mellow set..The jam following seastones is sublime..5 for the music 4.5 for sound quality...thanks guys.
